    },
    {
      "text": "\nFor decades, fully automatic weapons were expensive, collectable, and rarely used in crimes. Auto sears, which can cost less than $20 online, have changed that.\n\nThe Return of the Machine Gun\n\nRead the story\n\n\n\n\n\n\n",
